Q2 recursive function to count the number of external nodes 

Algorithm countExternal(n) :
	Input: a node n in the tree
	Output: Integer (number of external nodes)
	
	if isExternal(n) then
		return 1
		
	else 
		count=0
		if n.hasLeft then
			count = count + countExternal(n.left)
			
		if n.hasRight then
			count = count + countExternal(n.right)
			
	return count
	
	
